HB 332 Original 2026 Regular Session Turner
Abstract: Provides for requirements relative to the frequency of meetings of the Louisiana
Agricultural Finance Authority.
Present law creates the La. Agricultural Finance Authority and requires that it meet at least
four, but not more than 12 times a year upon call.
Proposed law modifies present law by reducing the minimum number of meetings per year
from four to two.
Effective upon signature of governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
(Amends R.S. 3:264(H))
